@wp.kernel
def rand_expr_kzbpfi(data: wp.array(dtype=float)):
    tid = wp.tid()
    v0 = data[tid]
    v1 = 0.0
    v2 = 1.0
    tmp = 0.0
    v2 = ((wp.exp(v0 + 0.37) * tmp) + (0.42 + wp.abs(v0 + 0.14)))
    v2 = v1
    v2 = 0.28
    v0 = (wp.exp(v2) - (0.10 + wp.sin(v2 + 0.71)))
    v2 = v1
    data[tid] = v0
